Requirements:

   SDL

To configure:

   ./autogen.sh
   LDFLAGS="-L`psp-config --pspsdk-path`/lib -lc -lpspglue -lpspuser" \
     ./configure --host psp --with-sdl-prefix=`psp-config --pspsdk-path`/.. \
     --disable-music-mp3 --prefix=`psp-config --pspsdk-path`/..

Then run:

   make
   make install
